，過伯公坳後落斜啲景幾靚</blockquote><br />\n有興 details pls</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/transport/roadandtraffic/lantaupermit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Ftransport%2Froadandtraffic%2Flantaupermit.htm&d=pcNoLc4C6sRk%2BPJsHU10M8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e834a3c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/transport/roadandtraffic/lantaupermit.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長沙就<br />\n下長沙先有野食 個入口有啲隱蔽<br />\n另外<br />\n梅窩出返東涌有一個影30嘅相機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多唔多牛？聽講有時要等牛群過完馬路先行得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4630181f64e424bb6fc18607a65b47585a3065","tid":379394,"uid":59046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>長沙brunch -&gt;昂平-&gt;大澳-&gt;梅窩晚餐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攞日week day off申請禁區紙去<br />\n<br />\n利申： 揸過，過伯公坳後落斜啲景幾靚</blockquote><br />\n有興 details pls</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/transport/roadandtraffic/lantaupermit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Ftransport%2Froadandtraffic%2Flantaupermit.htm&d=pcNoLc4C6sRk%2BPJsHU10M8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e834a3c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/transport/roadandtraffic/lantaupermit.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長沙就<br />\n下長沙先有野食 個入口有啲隱蔽<br />\n另外<br />\n梅窩出返東涌有一個影30嘅相機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多唔多牛？聽講有時要等牛群過完馬路先行得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日落後夜晚多<br />\n見過15-20隻坐/訓係馬路 封左成條線@水口<br />\n又或者到日落 長沙會突然有幾十隻牛行左落沙灘訓<br />\n<br />\n日間無乜<br />\n<br />\nbtw <br />\n水牛就唔好惹 隻角大有啲危險<br />\n黃牛d角細好多 佢撞你都無咁傷"},{"pid":"0789900464994e6e38ce2f41d41770d49a2b713c","tid":379394,"uid":82915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大尾篤，食個tea，